title: The Milky Way
description:
Victor Wong (sfe-co2) posted a photo:

The Milky Way photographed at Wisemans Ferry, New South Wales, Sydney, on 7-5-2016. First attempt at night sky photography.

Despite working in near total darkness, some city light contamination is still evident after processing, though not immediately apparent during the lonely shoot (out in the middle of nowahere, with RJ Wong).

Some evening fog was starting to move across (lower orange feature that caught the city lights).
author: nobody@flickr.com (Victor Wong (sfe-co2))
